headline: The Serverlist: Serverless Computing vs. Containers, Serverless MySQL at Scale, and more!
keywords: The Serverlist Newsletter, Serverless, Cloudflare Workers
description: Check out our sixteenth edition of The Serverlist below. Get the latest scoop on the serverless space, get your hands dirty with new developer tutorials, engage in conversations with other serverless developers, and find upcoming meetups and conferences to attend.
